title: Do The Math (2013) - Bill McKibben Documentary on Climate Change
description:
From IMDB:

"DO THE MATH chronicles environmentalist Bill McKibben in a David-vs-Goliath battle to fight the fossil fuel industry and change the terrifying math of the climate crisis.

Bill McKibben is going after Big Oil, Big Coal, and Big Gas directly - energizing a movement like the ones that overturned the great immoral institutions of the past century."

running time 44m52s

Stop the Alberta tar sands!
